<p>Cookies Policy</p><p><br></p><p>Last updated: February 11, 2026</p><p><br></p><p>UserVault uses cookies and similar tracking technologies to provide and improve our services.</p><p><br></p><p>What Are Cookies?</p><p><br></p><p>Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. They help us remember your preferences, authenticate your session, and analyze platform usage.</p><p><br></p><p>Types of Cookies We Use</p><p><br></p><p>1. Essential Cookies (Required)</p><p>• Authentication: Keep you logged in</p><p>• Security: Protect against fraud and attacks</p><p>• Preferences: Remember your settings (language, theme)</p><p><br></p><p>2. Analytics Cookies (Optional)</p><p>• Usage tracking: Understand how users interact with our platform</p><p>• Performance monitoring: Identify and fix issues</p><p>• Feature analytics: Measure adoption of new features</p><p><br></p><p>3. Advertising Cookies (Optional)</p><p>• Ad personalization: Show relevant advertisements</p><p>• Conversion tracking: Measure ad effectiveness</p><p>• Retargeting: Display ads on other websites</p><p><br></p><p>Third-Party Cookies</p><p><br></p><p>We use services that may set their own cookies:</p><p>• Google Analytics (usage analysis)</p><p>• Payment processors (transaction security)</p><p>• Advertising networks (ad delivery)</p><p><br></p><p>Managing Cookies</p><p><br></p><p>You can control cookies through:</p><p>• Browser settings: Block or delete cookies</p><p>• Opt-out tools: Disable tracking from specific services</p><p>• UserVault settings: Manage cookie preferences (coming soon)</p><p><br></p><p>Note: Disabling essential cookies may affect platform functionality.</p><p><br></p><p>Cookie Duration</p><p><br></p><p>• Session cookies: Deleted when you close your browser</p><p>• Persistent cookies: Remain for a specified period (up to 1 year)</p><p><br></p><p>Changes to This Policy</p><p><br></p><p>We may update this Cookies Policy to reflect changes in technology or regulations.</p><p><br></p><p>Contact Us</p><p><br></p><p>For questions about cookies, contact us at: privacy@uservault.net</p><p><br></p>